description: Redevelopment to provide a three and four story housing scheme of 66 units with 20 parking spaces and a two storey Medical Centre with 6 parking spaces.The housing will comprise - 28 No. 1-bedroom flats; 1 No. 1-bedroom house; 21 No. 2-bedroom flats; 15 No. 3-bedroom maisonettes and 1 No. 4-bedroom maisonette and extension to Lavina Grove northward to join All Saints Street. Applicant's Plan Nos: 9214/P/20A-29A  9215/9/10C  9/11C 18D  SK72C  SK73B.
decision_conditions: To comply with the provisions of Section 91(1) of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
